{"tid":1054833,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"經濟未見起色！強國2月汽車銷量暴減18.5%","createTime":"2019-03-10T06:36:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-11T23:22:01.000Z","uid":54733,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"00f23114c863730c0f881e637949cf719f23f479","tid":1054833,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T06:36:53.000Z","msg":"經濟未見起色！內地2月汽車銷量驟減18.5%<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190308/photo/bkn-20190308163402937-0308_00842_001_01p.jpg?20190308171319\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20190308%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190308163402937-0308_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20190308171319&h=f5d0c49e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國全國乘用車市場信息聯席會公布，中國2月廣義乘用車零售銷量119萬輛，按年大幅減少18.5%，已連續第9個月減少，並大幅高於1月按年減少4%。<br />\n<br />\n由於內地汽車銷售佔整體消費約一成，為「經濟晴雨表」，目前數據仍不濟，反映經濟依然未見起色。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190308/bkn-20190308163402937-0308_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20190308%2Fbkn-20190308163402937-0308_00842_001.html&d=hArt0m4UYatnQvENVNvF2Flsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=b84560a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190308/bkn-20190308163402937-0308_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"af044c974f841a0c9a9db2e8d02bf7e9ecb5522f","tid":1054833,"uid":34655,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T07:12:20.000Z","msg":"說好的內需呢"},{"pid":"9ccca8ecdce11b370eb1e22cdc4339f2654f6712","tid":1054833,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T07:14:28.000Z","msg":"跌咁少"},{"pid":"2332415ebc7d0216a4de61881a2d3fc0df4dffad","tid":1054833,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T07:14:46.000Z","msg":"等睇有傻鳩話今年二月新年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdc0ef7201fa383df89a8ec9844059d9838f36a1","tid":1054833,"uid":52946,"like":3,"dislike"